      <title>高盛筹集 210 亿美元建立其最大私人信贷池</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/goldman-racks-up-21-billion-for-its-largest-private-credit-pool</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团已为私人信贷投资筹集了 210 亿美元，这是该集团迄今为止为华尔街最热门的资产类别投入的最大一笔资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/goldman-racks-up-21-billion-for-its-largest-private-credit-pool</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
