      <title>欧盟计划于 6 月底启动乌克兰入盟谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/eu-aims-to-start-ukraine-membership-negotiations-by-end-of-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟计划最早于 6 月 25 日与乌克兰开始谈判，成为欧盟成员国，以帮助提振基辅的士气，但尚未完全克服匈牙利的反对意见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/eu-aims-to-start-ukraine-membership-negotiations-by-end-of-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BMO 盈利因拨备高于预期而低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bmo-earnings-miss-estimates-on-higher-than-expected-provisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者和企业难以应对更高的利率，蒙特利尔银行为应对潜在信贷损失拨备了比预期更多的资金，因此该银行的业绩不及分析师预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bmo-earnings-miss-estimates-on-higher-than-expected-provisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
